<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="escape-v">escape <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'skeɪp/    美 /ɪ'skeɪp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>逃走；逃跑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hunter tried to <strong>escape from</strong> the forest, but he lost his way. 
猎人试图逃出森林，但是迷路了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>逃脱；逃避：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>escape sb’s attention</strong> / <strong>notice</strong>
逃过某人的注意；被某人忽视</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A boy <strong>escaped unhurt</strong> when the fire in his room exploded.
房间里发生火灾时男孩逃了出来，没有受伤。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>narrowly escaped</strong> death in an earthquake. 
他在一次地震中死里逃生。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>escape doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You are lucky to escape being punished. 
你逃脱了惩罚，真走运。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>(气体、液体等) 泄露：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A small hole allowed smoke to escape from the top.
一个小孔能让烟从顶部冒出来。</p><footer>2010 福建</footer></div></div>